<div class="container mb-5">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-header text-center">
          <h4>Essential</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body text-left">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h4>$49 per month*</h4>
            <span class="text-muted">VAT not included, try it free for 14 days</span>
          </div>
          <p>Startups and small engineering teams.</p>
          <hr/>
          <p>💬 GitHub Checks annotations with coverage warnings and diff summary</p>
          <p>🌳 Branch coverage</p>
          <p>📦 2500 builds per month for private repos (with 2 concurrent builds at a time)</p>
          <p>♾️ Unlimited users</p>
          <br/>
          <% if current_user.nil? %>
            <p class="text-center">
              <%= link_to "Sign Up with GitHub", "/auth/github?r=sign_up", class: "btn btn-md btn-primary", method: :post %>
            </p>
          <% else %>
            <p class="text-center">
              <%= link_to "Start subscription", settings_path, class: "btn btn-md btn-primary" %>
            </p>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="card mb-4 shadow-lg">
        <div class="card-header text-center">
          <h4>Plus</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body text-left">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h4>$249 per month*</h4>
            <span class="text-muted">VAT not included, try it free for 14 days</span>
          </div>
          <p>Medium to large engineering teams.</p>
          <hr/>
          <p>Includes everything in Essential, plus:</p>
          <p>📊 Metrics dashboards to track coverage trends per repository</p>
          <p></p>
          <p>♾️ Unlimited check builds for private repos</p>
          <p>♾️ Unlimited concurrent check builds</p>
          <p>♾️ Unlimited users</p>
          <br/>
          <% if current_user.nil? %>
            <p class="text-center">
              <%= link_to "Sign Up with GitHub", "/auth/github?r=sign_up", class: "btn btn-md btn-primary", method: :post %>
            </p>
          <% else %>
            <p class="text-center">
              <%= link_to "Start subscription", settings_path, class: "btn btn-md btn-primary" %>
            </p>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-header text-center">
          <h4>Open Source</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body text-left">
          <p>Undercover is built on <b>open-source</b> and is free to use for public GitHub repositories. <%= link_to "Sign Up with GitHub", "/auth/github?r=sign_up", method: :post %> to get started.</p>
          <p>If a hosted GitHub App integration won't work for you, check out these links to get started and with local and CI/CD workflows:</p>
          <ul>
            <p>🔗 <a href="https://medium.com/@mrgrodo/improve-your-ruby-code-reviews-with-actionable-code-coverage-and-undercover-c4480575ea69">Improve your Ruby code reviews with actionable code coverage and Undercover</a>
            <p>🔗 <a href="https://github.com/grodowski/undercover">grodowski/undercover</a></p>
            <p>🔗 <a href="https://github.com/grodowski/pronto-undercover">grodowski/pronto-undercover</a></p>
            <p>🔗 <a href="https://github.com/nimblehq/danger-undercover">nimblehq/danger-undercover</a></p>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col text-center my-3">
      <p class="small mt-2">
        * yearly discounts available for all plans by default
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
